alerts.description: Widespread slippery conditions on the ground are expected due to: 3 to 5 cm fresh snow in 1 hour, or 6 to 10 cm fresh snow in 6 hours, or 11 to 25 cm fresh snow in 24 hours, or widespread black ice or ice patches. Be careful and follow the instructions of the responsible authority.
